How Tironem Quickly Connects You with Top Talent

Prepare

Tironem's powerful AI generates interview questions based on job titles and descriptions, or adapts to your specific inputs.

Pre-Screen

Tironem's powerful AI generates interview questions questions (in an Australian accent) in the flow and feel of a real meeting.

Assess

The real magic begins with intelligent, real-time assessment of answers.Tironem adapts to responses and gathers the best insights.

Connect

You can now connect with a refined list of top talent - and you've just saved yourself hours (or days) of tedious vetting time.

The Easy Way to Fill Positions with AI Recruitment Software

The hiring process doesn't need to be a chore - for you or your job applicants.

Candidates apply for roles through existing job boards. Those who match your criteria move on to a video interview with your Tironem AI recruiter co-pilot.

Applicants engage in a natural, verbal exchange as Tironem analyses and adapts to responses. You can then focus on the top talent without spending hours sifting through them.

A Beautiful Balance of Speed and Flexibility

Tironem works faster than you thought was possible, transcribing and evaluating every video interview.

At the same time, you maintain control over checking, reviewing, and digging into the details of recorded meetings.

Tironem learns from your feedback, continuously improving the speed and accuracy of candidate recommendations.

It's Time - to Save Time and Lower Your Cost of Acquisition

Stop spending hours or days wading through the sea of unsuitable resumes.

Let Tironem help you discover top talent - without the heavy lifting.

Hire faster, lower your cost of acquisition, and fill positions with high-quality candidates.
